title: 90: Their Opinions Don't Matter
description:
Today's episode is some straight up TRUTH that I hope you really understand. The number one thing that holds people back from being everything they can be, are people's opinions. After this episode, I know that is something that will no longer control your life. Let's get it!

Make sure you hit me up on Instagram with your biggest takeaways.
